Package build checklist for irlba
---------------------------------

I. If no changes to C code in src/ directory, then

  1. Locally run:

     R CMD build irlba
     R CMD check --as-cran irlba_x.x.x.tar.gz

  2. If step 1. passes, upload to R winbuilder and check against at least
     R-devel, see https://win-builder.r-project.org/upload.aspx.

  3. If step 2. passes, then OK to submit to CRAN.



II. After changes to C code in src/ directory, then

  1. Locally run rchk, see https://github.com/kalibera/rchk.

  2. Goto step I. above.
